1. "*Deda* je učio decu da se uvek ponašaju kako treba." (Grandfather taught the children to always behave properly.)
2. "*Dedi* je bilo lepo da dođe na proslavu." (It was nice of Grandpa to come to the celebration.)
3. "*Dede* je ljubilo da vozi bicikl." (Grandpa loved to ride a bike.)
4. "*Deda* mi je pokazao kako da napravim zabavu za drugu decu." (Grandfather showed me how to make a party for other children.)
5. "*Dedi* je donelo puno zabave na rođendan." (Granddad brought a lot of fun to the birthday.)